OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather cloudy and damp
OL,6,Fmorning with outbreaks of rain,
OL,7,Fpotentially turning heavy at first.
OL,8,FThe rain easing, leaving a mostly dry
OL,9,Fafternoon but staying largely cloudy
OL,10,Fwith only a few brighter breaks.
OL,11,FFeeling warm and humid despite the
OL,12,Fcloud.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FA mostly dry evening and
OL,15,Fnight across the region with some
OL,16,Fclear intervals developing, especially
OL,17,Ftowards the north. Staying humid
OL,18,Fallowing some mist and low cloud to
OL,19,Fform.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
