OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA grey and potentially murky
OL,6,Fstart, however cloud will gradually
OL,7,Fthin and break allowing skies to
OL,8,Fbrighten. Some sunny spells developing
OL,9,Fduring the afternoon, especially in
OL,10,Fthe southeast. Feeling warm.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMostly
OL,13,Fdry on Friday with bright spells. A
OL,14,Fchance of some showers on Saturday,
OL,15,Fthen fine on Sunday. Feeling very warm
OL,16,Fby day, with nights also staying warm
OL,17,Fand humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
